HASP_UPDATE_TOO_OLD

public static final int HASP_UPDATE_TOO_OLD
Trying to install a V2C file with an update counter that is out of sequence with the update counter on the HASP SRM protection key. The update counter value in the V2C file is lower than the value in HASP SRM protection key.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

HASP_UPDATE_TOO_NEW

public static final int HASP_UPDATE_TOO_NEW
Trying to install a V2C file with an update counter that is out of sequence with update counter in the HASP SRM protection key. The first value in the V2C file is greater than the value in the HASP SRM protection key.
